Loop continues until the correct number is guessed

ğŸ§  How It Works

The program generates a random number between 1 and 100.

The user enters a guess.

The program compares the guess with the secret number:

Too high â†’ shows hint

Too low â†’ shows hint

The game ends when the correct number is guessed.

